1000 she was instrumental in masterminding the creation of the 
/ARTICLEREF /REFNAME ../DungeonMaster/CouncilOfTwelve.html /REFTEXT Council Of Twelve REFTEXT/ ARTICLEREF/  which was 
convened in order to deal with invasion. She is however extremely reluctant to spend money and has consistently 
advocated the minimization of spending on Tisloch's army. Especially since the victories of 1003 she has insisted 
on cutting back on military spending, putting her at odds with 
